# Compiled host-test binaries (g++ output from running tests locally/in CI).
# Pattern-based so a NEW test_*.cpp's binary is ignored automatically — the
# per-name list previously missed test_acquire (#386) and left an untracked
# binary after every local run. Sources are kept; only the extensionless
# compiled outputs are ignored.
test_*
!test_*.cpp
!test_*.h
